videos.description: Damian Lillard drops off a nice pass to a cutting Jusuf Nurkic, who goes up to finish a stylish reverse layup for Portland.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lillard finds Nurkic for sweet reverse finger roll) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lillard finds Nurkic for sweet reverse finger roll

videos.description: Andre Drummond gets an easy dunk as Anthony Davis finds him with a nice wrap-around pass under the basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD drops sweet dime to Drummond for the finish) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD drops sweet dime to Drummond for the finish

videos.description: Damian Lillard gets the pass from CJ McCollum and pulls up from just in front of the Blazers' logo to knock down a dead-eye 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dame drains deep 3 in front of the logo) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dame drains deep 3 in front of the logo

videos.description: Damian Lillard uses the screen then slips in between Lakers defenders to put down an easy dunk in the lane for the Blazers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lillard weaves between defenders for easy slam) 2021/05/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lillard weaves between defenders for easy slam

videos.description: Damian Lillard goes off for 38 points on 12-of-18 shooting from the field and leads the Trail Blazers to a 106-101 victory over the Lakers at home.
